Author: Q Kodda <qkodda@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Nov 27 22:21:21 2025 -0500

    Add Streak Squares feature with metrics tracking and UI polish
    
    Streak Squares Feature (Client-side v1):
    - Added 2x2 grid (now horizontal scroll) of metric squares below Calendar section
    - Tracks 4 metrics: Ideas Generated, Ideas Scheduled, Scheduling Streak, Session Streak
    - Client-side persistence using localStorage (phazee_streak_data)
    - Consecutive day streak logic with YYYY-MM-DD date normalization
    - Scale bump animation (400ms ease-out) on value increase
    - ARIA accessible with role=status and aria-live=polite
    
    Visual Design:
    - Black containers (84x84px) with gradient text (var(--gradient-tiffany))
    - Horizontal scrollable row aligned to left edge of collapsed cards
    - Hidden scrollbar with smooth touch scrolling
    - Number font: 22px, Label font: 9px
    - 12px gap between squares, 8px border-radius
    
    Integration Points:
    - Ideas Generated: wired to generateNewIdeas() batch reveal loop
    - Ideas Scheduled: wired to confirmScheduleDate() success handler
    - Session Streak: updates on navigateTo('homepage')
    - Scheduling Streak: tracks consecutive scheduling days
    
    Text Improvements:
    - Singular/plural handling: '1 Day' vs '2 Days'
    - Shows '0 Days' instead of just '0'
    - Dynamic labels based on streak state
    
    Additional Fixes:
    - Aligned settings/help buttons with collapsed card right edge (340px width)
    - Reduced hero greeting top padding to 0px
    - Moved swipe cards flush to top (removed 25px offset)
    - Centered background shadow cards vertically with idea cards
    - Moved swiper-info up 30px for tighter spacing
    
    Non-destructive Implementation:
    - Zero backend/auth/database changes
    - No dev-bypass modifications
    - All existing features preserved
    - Works in current phazee-global-rename branch

